  ```python
  @app.route('/venue/<int:venue_id>')
  def view_venue(venue_id):
      # ...
      return render_template('view-venue-details.html', venue_id=venue_id)
  ```
  And inside `view-venue-details.html`, use the `venue_id` variable to display details.

- Verify all template files are present and correctly named.
- Restart your Flask app after adding or renaming templates.

